{"title":"Unity Shader入门精要笔记 - Chapter9","uid":"56562ce640a8509a88d7ae0465a97a36","slug":"Technical Artist/Unity/UnityShaderTutorial/Chapter9/Chapter9","date":"2023-03-08T13:29:05.000Z","updated":"2023-03-08T13:45:38.814Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Technical Artist/Unity/UnityShaderTutorial/Chapter9/Chapter9.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JBR-Bunjie/JBR-Bunjie/main/back.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"Chapter-9-更复杂的光照-more-complex-lights\"><a href=\"#Chapter-9-更复杂的光照-more-complex-lights\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Chapter 9: 更复杂的光照 - more complex lights\"></a>Chapter 9: 更复杂的光照 - more complex lights</h1><h2 id=\"1-渲染路径\"><a href=\"#1-渲染路径\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.渲染路径\"></a>1.渲染路径</h2><p>关于书中提及的与编译指令 <code>pragma multi_compile_fwdbase</code> 类似的官方文档：<a href=\"https://docs.unity3d.com/Manual/SL-MultipleProgramVariants.html\">Unity - Manual: Declaring and using shader keywords in HLSL (unity3d.com)</a></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>关于 <code>shader variant</code>，可以参考这篇文章：<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/369425274\">unity ShaderVariants处理 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>You can write <strong>shader</strong> snippets that share common code, but have different functionality when a given keyword is enabled or disabled. </p>\n<p>When Unity compiles these shader snippets, it creates separate shader programs for the different combinations of enabled and disabled keywords. These individual shader programs are called shader variants.</p></blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<p>简单来说，这种操作类似于，我们通过在Shader运行时动态的改变宏(这里是 <code>Keyword</code>)的方式来动态得到我们需要的结果。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.